{%- comment -%}-----------------------------------------------------------------

Design Pattern:
  [_util-json-get-type-from-xjson]

Snippet:
  _util-json-get-type-from-xjson.Liquid

Usage:
  {% capture type %}
    {% render "_util-json-get-type-from-xjson", xjson: xjson %}
  {% endcapture %}

Parameters:
  {string} xjson

Output:
  - A string with the type-tag of the XJSON.

Description:
  - The type-tag is found in the meta-head of the XJSON string:

        XJSON --> meta || data
          meta --> type-tag | data-delimiter

--------------------------------------------------------------{%- endcomment -%}

{%- liquid
  assign arr_xjson = xjson | split: "||"
  assign meta = arr_xjson[0]
  assign arr_meta = meta | split: "|"
  assign type = arr_meta[0]

  echo type
-%}
